# ── Production Image Manifest ─────────────────────────────────
# This file controls which image digests/tags are deployed to production.
# Update via PR → review → merge → auto-deploy.
#
# To promote new images:
#   1. Wait for staging to be updated automatically after main CI/CD
#   2. Edit BACKEND_IMAGE and/or FRONTEND_IMAGE to the desired sha-* tag
#   3. Open PR, review, approve, and merge
#   4. The production CD workflow deploys automatically
#
# Images should use immutable tags (sha-<gitsha>) to avoid drift.
#
# Format: ghcr.io/hyka-tech-ductifact/<service>:sha-<gitsha>
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

RELEASE_VERSION=v0.0.0

BACKEND_IMAGE=-
FRONTEND_IMAGE=-
